232a				; poke the stub of the word list linked list to repoint to rom words 
232a			 
232a				; stub format 
232a				; db   word id 
232a				; dw    link to next word 
232a			        ; db char length of token 
232a				; db string + 0 term 
232a				; db exec code....  
232a			 
